          <title>NYPD Chief John Chell discusses security plans for Oct. 7</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NEW YORK (PIX11) – Monday marks one year since Hamas’ deadly attack on Israel.  On Oct. 7, 2023, Hamas-led militants killed some 1,200 people, mostly civilians, in an attack in southern Israel and took around 250 hostage. Some 100 are still held, around 65 of whom are believed to be alive.]]></description>
